snippet: Before each Giants game, Jennings executes a 25-minute routine that is part performance art, part plyometrics and part flexibility training. He calls it “body activation.”
lead_paragraph: Before each Giants game, Jennings executes a 25-minute routine that is part performance art, part plyometrics and part flexibility training. He calls it “body activation.”

headline.main: Rashad Jennings’s Inimitable, Elaborate Pre-Game Dance
